snippet.title: SPLIT Game Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Escape a bizarre, fractured world in SPLIT, where the world revolves around you!  Traverse a complex, geometric environment in this 2.5D puzzle platformer from up-and-coming indie game developer, Saluie Studios.

Coming in late April 2022.

Check us out on 
Twitter: @SaluieStudios
Instagram: saluiestudios
Website: https://saluiestudios.weebly.com/
